so&amp;client_id=vO1Kblk7xX9tUn2cpZLS&amp;dt=1741801019\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; display: inline;\">sign in</a>. Genius discounts at this property are subject to book dates, stay dates and other available deals.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: var(--bui_font_body_2_font-family); font-size: var(--bui_font_body_2_font-size); font-weight: var(--bui_font_body_2_font-weight); white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Nozol Royal Inn Hotel is 100 metres away from Al-Masjid al-Nabawi, a 10-minute drive from the public station. It offers an on-site restaurant with a 24-hour room service. The hotel offers free WiFi access.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>', 1, 63, NULL, '2025-03-12 17:37:39', '2025-03-12 17:37:39', 4),
(66, 'Emaar Taibah Madinah', 'Madinah', '<p>\r\n	Emaar Taiba Hotel in Al Madinah offers a central position with Al-Masjid an-Nabawi just a 02-minute walk away. Rooms feature air-conditioning, private bathrooms with walk-in showers, bidets, refrigerators, free toiletries, showers, TVs, and wardrobes. Additional amenities include electric kettles.</p>', 1, NULL, '1747420840-hotel-.webp', '2025-05-16 17:51:59', '2025-05-16 18:40:40', 3),
