(106, 'Pyramids Hotel', 'Cairo', '<p>\r\n	<strong>About this property</strong><br />\r\n	<strong>Comfortable Accommodations: </strong>Pyramids Hotel in Al Haram offers family rooms with air-conditioning, private bathrooms, and balconies with mountain or city views. Each room includes a work desk, TV, and free WiFi.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Dining and Leisure:</strong> Guests can enjoy a sun terrace, restaurant, bar, and coffee shop. The family-friendly restaurant serves African, British, Italian, and Middle Eastern cuisines, while the bar provides a relaxing atmosphere.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Convenient Location: </strong>Located 31 km from Cairo International Airport, the hotel is an 18-minute walk from the Great Sphinx. Nearby attractions include Giza Pyramids (2 km) and Cairo Tower (14 km).</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Guest Services: </strong>The hotel offers free on-site parking, a 24-hour front desk, concierge service, and a tour desk. Additional amenities include a lounge, minimarket, and outdoor play area.</p>', 1, 1, '1748603701-hotel-.jpg', '2025-05-30 06:15:01', '2025-05-30 06:15:01', 3);
