RING<br>\r\n                   <strong>£ 1025</strong></td>\r\n           <td data-label=\"NOTED\" valign=\"top\">Direct flights can be arranged on special request.<br>\r\n             Ground transfer can be included on extra cost.</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n           <td data-label=\"TOTAL DAYS\" valign=\"top\">14 NIGHTS SEPTEMBER UMRAH PACKAGES</td>\r\n           <td data-label=\"PACKAGE INCLUDED\" valign=\"top\">FLIGHTS : INCLUDED, VISA : INCLUDED, 24/7 CUSTOMER SUPPORT,BEST HOTELS AND EMAIL SUPPORT</td>\r\n           <td data-label=\"HOTELS\" valign=\"top\">7 NIGHTS IN MAKKAH WITH 5 STAR HOTELS<strong> (Pullman Zamzam Hotel)  </strong>7 NIGHTS IN MADINA WITH 5 STAR HOTELS<br>\r\n<strong>(Crowne Plaza Medina hotel)</strong>\r\n           </td>\r\n           <td data-label=\"PRICES\" valign=\"top\">PACKAGE ARE BASED ON 4 PEOPLE SHARING<br>\r\n                   <strong>£ 1315</strong></td>\r\n           <td data-label=\"NOTED\" valign=\"top\">Direct flights can be arranged on special request.<br>\r\n             Ground transfer can be included on extra cost.</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n       </tbody>\r\n</table>', NULL, 5, 1, '1', '2025-03-10 13:01:09', '2025-03-10 13:01:09');
