nal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">You can choose from 3-star, 4-star, or 5-star Umrah packages, and adjust your stay length from 1 week to 15 days.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Our team works closely with you to personalize flights, transport, and amenities, ensuring a smooth and spiritually fulfilling journey that aligns with your budget and comfort.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">All-Inclusive Umrah Packages with Flights</span></h3>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Make your pilgrimage completely stress-free with our Umrah packages, all-inclusive of flights, visa, hotel, and transport. These Umrah packages, including flights, are ideal for UK travelers who want a single, comprehensive solution without the hassle of separate bookings.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">We cover every detail, from ticket booking to airport transfers, so you can focus solely on your spiritual journey.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Available across multiple seasons, including October, November, and December, Umrah packages, our all-in-one options suit solo travelers, couples, and groups.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Choose from cheap Umrah packages, budget Umrah packages, or luxury Umrah packages, all designed to offer value, comfort, and convenience in one place.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Ready to Begin Your Journey?</span></h2>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Explore Umrah packages designed around your comfort, even if you prefer a short 7-day trip or a deeper 14-day spiritual experience.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Haq Travels handles every detail, allowing you to stay focused on your worship. With easy booking and full support from the UK, your journey is guided with care and reliability.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Take the first step today and let Haq Travels guide you every step of your way to Umrah. Your meaningful pilgrimage begins here.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Frequently Asked Questions:</span></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">How much does it cost to go on Umrah?</span></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">The cost of Umrah depends on the package and travel dates. At Haq Travels, our Umrah packages start from </span>[&pound;600: will be updated] for 7 nights and [&pound;700: will be updated] for 14 nights. Each package includes flights, accommodation near the Haram, and transport. You can explore all options here: Haq Umrah Packages</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">How much is the ticket for Umrah?</span></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Flight ticket prices for Umrah vary depending on the season and airline.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Typically, return flights from the UK range from &pound;500 to &pound;800, but when you book through Haq Travels, flight costs are already included in our all-in-one Umrah packages.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Can I do Umrah with UK BRP?</span></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Yes, you can perform Umrah with a valid UK Biometric Residence Permit (BRP).&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">You will need to apply for an Umrah visa separately, which we can assist you with during the booking process.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Which is the cheapest month for Umrah?</span></h4>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">The most affordable months for Umrah are usually after Hajj season, especially during Muharram and Safar, and before Ramadan begins.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e9a4a030-7fff-3ddf-c8c0-c80862a5de1d\">Prices are lower during off-peak months, and you can find the best value deals with us during this time.</span></p>', 'home', '', 'Cheap Umrah Packages', 'Discover cheap Umrah packages from the UK for 7 to 14 nights. Book your seamless Umrah journey from the UK with Haq Travels; flights, accommodation, and dedicated support are included.', NULL, 1, 1, '2024-07-16 08:39:08', '2025-05-28 17:44:41', 0, NULL),
(2, 'Experience the Holiness of Umrah & Hajj with Haq Travels', '<h4>\r\n	<b>UNDERSTANDING THE IMPORTANCE OF UMRAH AND HAJJ</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Delve into the significance of Umrah &amp; Hajj in the Islamic faith. Hajj is one of the Five Pillars of Islam and represents a spiritual journey to the holy city of Makkah, whereas Umrah is a lesser pilgrimage that can be performed at any time of the year.<br />\r\n	Explore the spiritual benefits and rewards associated with these sacred journeys. Hajj and Umrah offer believers the opportunity to seek forgiveness, strengthen their faith, and experience a deep connection with Allah.<br />\r\n	Learn about the historical and religious context of Hajj and Umrah, including the rituals, traditions, and the importance of visiting the Kaaba, Safa and Marwa, and other sacred sites.</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Why Choose Haq Travels for Your Pilgrimage?</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Discover the reasons that make Haq Travels the ideal choice for your Umrah &amp; Hajj experience. With our years of experience and expertise in organizing pilgrimage journeys, we have garnered a reputation for excellence and reliability.<br />\r\n	Experience our commitment to professionalism, reliability, and customer satisfaction. We prioritize your needs and strive to provide personalized attention and care throughout your pilgrimage.<br />\r\n	Benefit from our extensive knowledge and expertise in organizing Hajj and Umrah packages. We understand the intricacies of the pilgrimage, the necessary arrangements, and the best practices to ensure a seamless and fulfilling journey.</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Tailored Packages to Suit Your Needs</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Explore our diverse range of Umrah &amp; Hajj packages, designed to cater to the unique requirements of every pilgrim. Whether you are an individual, a family, or a group, we have packages that can be customized to fit your preferences, budget, and desired duration.<br />\r\n	Choose from different package durations, accommodation options, and transportation arrangements. We offer a variety of choices to ensure that your pilgrimage is tailored to your specific needs and preferences.<br />\r\n	Enjoy flexibility in customizing your pilgrimage journey according to your preferences. Our experienced team is dedicated to working closely with you to create a personalized itinerary that encompasses the rituals, sightseeing, and spiritual experiences you desire.</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Unparalleled Expertise and Guidance</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Experience the guidance of our experienced and knowledgeable team throughout your entire journey. From the moment you contact us until you return home, our experts will be available to provide advice, support, and answers to any questions you may have.<br />\r\n	Receive comprehensive information about the rituals, practices, and etiquettes of Umrah &amp; Hajj. Our team will ensure that you are well-prepared and equipped with the necessary knowledge to perform your pilgrimage in a respectful and meaningful manner.<br />\r\n	Feel reassured with our 24/7 assistance and support, ensuring a hassle-free pilgrimage. Our dedicated staff is just a phone call away, ready to address any concerns or emergencies that may arise during your journey.</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Hassle-Free Travel Arrangements</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Leave the travel logistics to us as we handle your visa processing, flight bookings, and transportation arrangements. Our experienced team is well-versed in the intricacies of travel planning and will ensure that all necessary arrangements are made with efficiency and accuracy.<br />\r\n	Benefit from our partnerships with reputable hotels and transportation providers, ensuring comfortable and convenient stays. We carefully select accommodations that are in close proximity to the sacred sites, allowing for easy access and a peaceful environment for reflection and worship.<br />\r\n	Enjoy a smooth and well-organized travel experience, allowing you to focus on your spiritual devotion. With our meticulous attention to detail and commitment to delivering exceptional service, we strive to eliminate any travel-related stress or distractions, enabling you to fully immerse yourself in your pilgrimage experience.</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Superior Accommodation and Transportation Services</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Rest comfortably in our carefully selected accommodations located in close proximity to the sacred sites. We understand the importance of providing a peaceful and comfortable place for you to rest and rejuvenate during your pilgrimage.<br />\r\n	Experience seamless transportation services that facilitate your movement between the holy cities of Makkah and Madinah. Our transportation arrangements are designed to ensure your safety, comfort, and convenience throughout your journey.<br />\r\n	Enjoy modern amenities and exceptional service during your stay, enhancing your overall pilgrimage experience. We prioritize your comfort and satisfaction, and our accommodations and transportation services are chosen with your needs in mind.</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"title-hr-left\">\r\n	Explore Our Range of Umrah and Hajj Packages</h3>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Hajj Packages:</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Immerse yourself in the comprehensive Hajj packages offered by Haq Travels, ensuring a transformative pilgrimage experience. Our Hajj packages are designed to provide you with a holistic journey that encompasses all the essential rituals and spiritual experiences.<br />\r\n	Choose from a variety of Hajj packages tailored to fit your budget, preferences, and the duration of your journey. We offer options that cater to both first-time pilgrims and those seeking a more in-depth and immersive experience.<br />\r\n	Benefit from accommodations situated near the sacred sites, allowing easy access to the rituals. We select hotels that provide a serene environment, enabling you to focus on your worship and reflection.</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Umrah Packages:</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Discover our well-organized and affordable Umrah packages , accommodating individuals, families, and groups. Our Umrah packages offer a simplified and hassle-free experience, allowing you to focus on the spiritual aspects of your pilgrimage.<br />\r\n	Enjoy flexibility in selecting the duration of your Umrah journey and the level of services you require. Whether you prefer a short and focused Umrah or an extended stay for additional spiritual activities, we have packages to suit your needs.<br />\r\n	Receive guidance and support from our experienced team, both in Makkah and Madinah. Our representatives will be there to assist you with any logistical or spiritual needs, ensuring a smooth and enriching pilgrimage experience.</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"title-hr-left\">\r\n	Haq Travels - Your Trusted Travel Agency for Umrah and Hajj</h3>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Years of Experience in Pilgrimage Services</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Trust in our extensive experience in organizing Umrah &amp; Hajj journeys, ensuring a smooth and memorable experience. We have been providing pilgrimage services for a significant period, establishing ourselves as a trusted and reputable travel agency in the industry.<br />\r\n	Benefit from our deep understanding of the religious and logistical aspects of the pilgrimage. Our team has accumulated a wealth of knowledge and expertise, enabling us to anticipate and address the unique challenges and requirements of Hajj and Umrah journeys.</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Team of Knowledgeable and Supportive Professionals</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Our dedicated team of experts is committed to providing personalized care and guidance. We understand the significance of your pilgrimage journey and are here to support you every step of the way.<br />\r\n	Receive assistance at every stage, from initial planning to the completion of your pilgrimage. Our knowledgeable staff will provide detailed information, answer your questions, and offer recommendations to ensure a fulfilling and spiritually uplifting experience.</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Strong Partnerships with Local Service Providers</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Leverage our strong relationships with local service providers to access top-quality accommodations, transportation, and other essential services. We have cultivated partnerships with trusted entities to ensure that you receive the highest standard of services during your pilgrimage.<br />\r\n	Enjoy exclusive benefits and seamless coordination through our established network. Our connections enable us to offer you competitive pricing, priority access to certain services, and a smooth and efficient experience throughout your journey.</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Personalized Customer Care and Assistance</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Experience our customer-centric approach, with a focus on understanding and fulfilling your unique needs. We take the time to listen to your requirements, preferences, and concerns, tailoring our services to ensure your utmost satisfaction.Receive prompt responses to your inquiries and ongoing support throughout your pilgrimage journey. Our dedicated customer care team is available 24/7, ensuring that you always have a reliable point of contact for any assistance you may require.</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Positive Testimonials from Satisfied Pilgrims</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Hear from our satisfied customers who have experienced the exceptional services provided by Haq Travels. Their testimonials reflect the trust, satisfaction, and spirituality they encountered during their pilgrimage.Read their testimonials on our website or request references to gain further insights into the transformative experiences that await you with Haq Travels.</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"title-hr-left\">\r\n	Plan Your Pilgrimage Today - Contact Haq Travels</h3>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Easy Booking Process</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Begin your journey by contacting our friendly and knowledgeable team, who will guide you through the booking process. We will provide you with all the necessary information and assistance to ensure a seamless and straightforward booking experience.<br />\r\n	Experience a streamlined and convenient booking system, ensuring a hassle-free start to your pilgrimage. Our goal is to simplify the process, making it accessible and convenient for all our clients.</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<b>Secure Your Spot in Our Exclusive Packages</b></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Reserve your place in our sought-after Umrah &amp; Hajj packages, which often have limited availability. By securing your spot early, you ensure that you have access to the best accommodations, flight options, and services.<br />\r\n	Benefit from early booking to secure preferred accommodations and flight options. Our team will work closely with you to understand your preferences and make the necessary arrangements to meet your expectations.</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"title-hr-left\">\r\n	Conclusion</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	Haq Travels is your reliable partner in making your Umrah &amp; Hajj dreams a reality. With our unwavering commitment to providing exceptional services, we ensure your pilgrimage journey is enriching, convenient, and spiritually rewarding. Book your Hajj or Umrah package with Haq Travels today and embark on a transformative spiritual experience. Trust us to handle the logistical details, allowing you to focus on the spiritual significance of this sacred journey.</p>', 'home-text-details', '', 'Experience the Holiness of Umrah & Hajj with Haq Travels', 'Experience the Holiness of Umrah & Hajj with Haq Travels', 'Experience the Holiness of Umrah & Hajj with Haq Travels', 2, 1, '2024-07-16 08:39:09', '2025-05-28 16:57:09', 0, NULL),
(3, 'About Us', '<h2>\r\n	Who We Are?</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	Haq Travels was established in 2020 with the aim of broadcasting and simplifying the sometimes complex Hajj and Umrah industry. Our Clever Technology enables us to compare a wide network of tour operators, airports and hotels to build a large number of Hajj and Umrah Packages to suit your needs. As a travel company with over 20 years of experience working on Hajj and Umrah packages, we are experienced in providing you with private and explicit advice on the blessed pilgrimage of Hajj or Umrah. Over the years we have helped thousands of customers through travel and thanks to the excellent feedback from our customers we have built a very good reputation in the industry. In addition to our Hajj and Umrah offerings, we can arrange &ldquo;halal holidays to Spain, Turkey, Morocco, Canada and Jordan as well as a guided tour to Masjid Al-Aqsa.</p>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Why Customers Prefer haqtravels.co.uk?</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	Experts in Hajj, Umrah and Islamic Tours, our travel advisors give you reliable and clear advice on planning and booking your trip and travel information itself. By the grace of Allah, we are focused on ensuring that our pilgrims are taught to the best of our ability during their pilgrimage and Umrah, but we will never pass a promise or fulfill it, we can choose to be faithful even when there is doubt in the promise and to bring more. The pilgrimage to Hajj and Umrah is unlike any other holiday so we believe that bespoke, one to one open service Weill ensures that customer expectations are clear. We have a wide variety of Hajj and Umrah Deals from budget to luxury and will be clear when something is budget and when something is luxury. We have met with many companies that will promise for example that a hotel is a 5 minute walk from a major mosque in Makkah or Medina and actually a trip is like 15 minutes. We believe it is best to tell the customer that the hotel is a 15 minute walk and the customer is happy if they can walk for 10 minutes. In addition, our company manages resources and has strong relationships with hotels in Makkah and Medina. We offer easy-to-use, affordable and affordable packages to meet the needs of everyone in the community. Our packages speak to all classes and citizens of the UK. Our services maintain a high level of speed, speed and reliability. Also, we have access to all flights to Saudi Arabia so you can be comfortable with your choice. Honesty and openness are key to haqtravels.co.uk</p>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Our Customer Care Facilities</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	Our tour guides will support you by planning and booking your trip and your trip to the sanctuary. We can help solve the problems facing our pilgrims from health issues to arranging ways to add transportation or sightseeing. We will have medicine / guides / staff present with us throughout our Hajj journey. Please call us on 0203 062 8925 if you are experiencing problems while traveling. We will also provide you with a Whatsapp contact while you are traveling to help you with any problems or to answer any questions. We look forward to seeing you soon!<br />\r\n	We look forward to making your journey memorable for you.</p>', 'about-us', NULL, 'About Us', NULL, NULL, 3, 1, '2024-07-17 02:37:38', '2025-03-06 05:33:55', 1, 0),
